<head><title>Internet Pinball Machine Database: Sonic 'Butterfly'</title>
<META HTTP-EQUIV="imagetoolbar" CONTENT="no">
<meta name="keywords" content="IPD IPDB Internet Pinball Machine Database Game Sonic Butterfly Flippers (2), Pop bumpers (2), Pop Up targets (3). 
Match number is last *three* digits of score.
Polyurethene playfield.

The object of the game is to knock down the three drop targets.  Each time the three targets are dropped, the playfield rollover stars are activated in the order B-U-T then T-E-R then F-L-Y.  When all the stars are lit, the scored climbs quickly.  ">
